\begin_layout Standard
§1.
 This was said by the Blessed One, said by the arahant, so I have heard:
 "I am a brahman, responsive to requests, open-handed, bearing my last body,
 an unsurpassed doctor & surgeon.
 You are my children, my sons, born from my mouth, born of the Dhamma, created
