 a certain person fabricates an uninjurious bodily fabrication...
 an uninjurious verbal fabrication...
 an uninjurious mental fabrication...
 He rearises in an uninjurious world where he is touched by uninjurious
 contacts...
 He experiences feelings that are exclusively pleasant, like those of the
 Ever-radiant Devas.
 This is called kamma that is bright with bright result.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
