 does not get involved.
 This is called the perception of distaste for every world.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
[9] "And what is the perception of the undesirability of all fabrications?
 There is the case where a monk feels horrified, humiliated, & disgusted
 with all fabrications.
 This is called the perception of the undesirability of all fabrications.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
[10] "And what is mindfulness of in-&-out breathing? There is the case where
