 it has been said.
 Why was it said?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"Birth is stressful, aging is stressful, death is stressful; sorrow, lamentation
, pain, distress, & despair are stressful; association with what is not
 loved is stressful, separation from what is loved is stressful, not getting
 what is wanted is stressful.
 In short, the five aggregates for sustenance are stressful.
