 cut it out with self-control, discernment, persistence, right view.
 The wise man would cut out each & every form of unskillfulness.
 Train yourselves: 'May we not be blotted out.' Free from anger & untroubled,
 free from greed, without longing, tamed, your anger abandoned, free from
 fermentation, you will be unbound.
\end_layout

