 & resolute — he in no long time reached & remained in the supreme goal
 of the holy life, for which clansmen rightly go forth from home into homelessne
ss, knowing & realizing it for himself in the here & now.
 He knew: "Birth is ended, the holy life fulfilled, the task done.
 There is nothing further for the sake of this world." And so Ven.
 Bharadvaja became another one of the arahants.
\end_layout

