§ 2.16.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"And what is ignorance? Not knowing stress, not knowing the origination
 of stress, not knowing the cessation of stress, not knowing the way of
 practice leading to the cessation of stress: This is called ignorance."
\end_layout

