"A person of integrity is endowed with qualities of integrity; he is a person
 of integrity in his friendship, in the way he wills, the way he gives advice,
 the way he speaks, the way he acts, the views he holds, & the way he gives
 a gift.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
