 skill...
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Whoever sees the world as having highs and lows doesn't yet have true intuitive
 discernment.
 Whoever has the eye of intuition will see that there are no highs, no lows,
 no rich, no poor.
 Everything is equal in terms of the three common characteristics: inconstant,
 stressful, and not-self.
 It's like the equality of democracy.
 Their home is the same as our home, with no differences at all.
 People commit burglaries and robberies these days because they don't see
