 power over the creations of others, the devas of Brahma's retinue, the
 devas beyond them.
 Whatever conviction they were endowed with that — when falling away from
 this life — they re-arose there, the same sort of conviction is present
 in me as well.
 Whatever virtue they were endowed with that — when falling away from this
 life — they re-arose there, the same sort of virtue is present in me as
