 Whatever learning they were endowed with that — when falling away from
 this life — they re-arose there, the same sort of learning is present in
 me as well.
 Whatever generosity they were endowed with that — when falling away from
 this life — they re-arose there, the same sort of generosity is present
 in me as well.
 Whatever discernment they were endowed with that — when falling away from
